{"tid":2174362,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人坐巴士返工覺得有一日會炒車","createTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T12:30:55.000Z","uid":104804,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"04d0952bac828a125de5880f4c6fbeced0f03ea2","tid":2174362,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:21:46.000Z","msg":"2017年1月14日晚上約9時，一輛行走東區海底隧道的城巴亞歷山大丹尼士Enviro500（8147／PH1273），駛至藍田鯉魚門道近藍田公共運輸交匯處出口對開，患有長期病患的六旬兼職車長懷疑突然病發失去知覺，巴士失控剷上路中石壆再向左翻側，橫亘慢線與行人路邊，造成1人死亡、18人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n唔知係唔係睇得死神來了多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b115126fc7de37afa89cb5db893e58b8135ec6f1","tid":2174362,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:24:38.000Z","msg":"2019年12月18日下午四時許，一輛行走過海隧巴978線往粉嶺（華明）方向的九巴Enviro500 MMC（ATENU341／TA6723）駛至粉嶺公路近古洞松柏朗，懷疑閃避一輛突然切線的泥頭車，失控撞向路邊大樹，上層左邊車身被削去，數名乘客被拋出車外，釀成6死39人傷。<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，同月同日過去亦曾發生車禍，詳見2015年錦田小巴意外。"},{"pid":"f39be1a934a3091382032574e7f2b33b24b48042","tid":2174362,"uid":1675,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"每次搭巴士<br />\n架車行天橋/近海就會諗架車會唔會衝落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5009e28c590d47fa3a6d6f6c1dc3a03024c85c7","tid":2174362,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f39be1a934a3091382032574e7f2b33b24b48042","tid":2174362,"uid":1675,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"每次搭巴士<br />\n架車行天橋/近海就會諗架車會唔會衝落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T00:39:35.000Z","msg":"轉彎個時坐上層<br />\n硬係覺得會跌落去咁"},{"pid":"d1b05d744fc8438decf8740f8e61e9547ad8a966","t